OFFICE OF THE HEADMASTER/HEADMISTRESS

Application for No Objection Certificate for Issue of Passport

This is to certify that the following statements regarding the applicant are true:

1. No disciplinary action has been taken or is pending against her.


2. No criminal or vigilance case is pending against her.


3. No allegations of serious offences or acts of alienation are pending against her.


4. There is no reason to believe that her record could adversely affect the security interests of the Government.



The application in the prescribed format and Annexure-M (in duplicate) is submitted herewith for your kind information and necessary action.

Signature of the Headmaster/Headmistress
